data.description: Take advantage of Sellers Assumable mortgage! Why wait for new construction? Here's your opportunity to own a massive, less than one year young, Upgraded 4 Level McPherson Model in the sought afterTimothy Branch community. Upon entering  this beautiful home you will find a first floor bedroom complete with a full bath and walk-in closet, a welcome center and an entrance to your spacious 2 car garage. As you walk upstairs you'll be greeted with a large open floor plan including a light filled living room, large dining room and beautifully appointed kitchen. The gourmet kitchen is full of upgrades including an over-sized island, double oven, gas cooktop, and quartz countertops. Off of the kitchen is a built in office nook and composite deck.  Gorgeous upgraded oak stairs can be found throughout. The third level features the owners suite with a large walk in closet and a spacious bathroom that includes double vanities, private toilet, and a large shower with dual shower heads and a bench.  Additionally you'll find 2 generously sized secondary bedrooms, laundry room and hall bath on this level. Head upstairs to your 4th level loft and separate 5th bedroom, this space is perfect for entertaining as it leads out to an expansive rooftop deck. The Timothy Branch community is a commuter-friendly neighborhood as it is conveniently located near many major routes including 301, Rte 5 and easy access to 495. The community features tot lots, club house, fitness center and a pool. Take advantage of Sellers Assumable mortgage! Schedule your tour today!
